Class OIndexTxAwareOneValue

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIndex<OIdentifiable>, Comparable<OIndex<OIdentifiable>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OIndexTxAwareDictionary

    public class OIndexTxAwareOneValue
extends OIndexTxAware<OIdentifiable>
    Transactional wrapper for indexes. Stores changes locally to the transaction until tx.commit(). All the other operations are delegated to the wrapped OIndex instance.
    Author:
    Luca Garulli
